                 THE RAINBOW POOL                                               Legend states that in some dimensions exist rare Rainbow Pools. These are       terrible teleporters which often attract the most horrible evils ever known.    Strange Lords of evil might have used them in the past to step in a world.      END                                                                             In so doing, the mighty titan-like beings could conquer at will, as they are    deemed the most powerful creatures in the universe. No one knows how to         de-activate such a pool to prevent entry of such beings.                        FINISH                                                                          